Dependencies
============

On Ubuntu all of these are available from package management:

sudo aptitude install python-nevow python-axiom python-magic python-tagpy

but beware a current bug:

http://divmod.org/trac/attachment/ticket/2770/axiom-indexed.diff

I applied this patch manually to:

	/usr/share/python-support/python-axiom/axiom/_schema.py

